# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

node_modules
dist
dist-ssr
*.local

# Feijoa = Cambridge display font, COMMERCIAL (Klim) — spec §12 / decision #18.
# Font files must NEVER be committed. Dropped in per Cambridge deploy only;
# Open Sans renders as the fallback until then. Keep the dir but ignore its fonts.
public/fonts/feijoa/*
!public/fonts/feijoa/README.md

# Editor directories and files
# Most .vscode/* is personal, but two files are shared so every clone gets the
# same out-of-the-box editor behaviour (format-on-save + recommended extensions).
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/settings.json
.idea
.DS_Store
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?
